Keywords: Market microstructure, asset pricing, market force, inertial frame of reference,
 accelerated frame of reference, (geometric) Brownian motion, Newtonian mechanics,
 Smoluchowski's approximation, optimal stochastic control, the Hamilton-Jacobi-Bellman
 equation, Markov property, Ornstein-Uhlenbeck process, Lévy process
